    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care typically reserved for private collections. Mechanically absolute and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering provides an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast.",
