    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve meticulously babied it since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for an uncompromising 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a traditional 6-speed manual Getrag transmission, the drivetrain is mechanically optimized with a recent comprehensive service including valve adjustments and rod bearing replacement. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity, complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Every suspension component remains taught, delivering the precise turn-in and communicative feedback synonymous with the M-division's peak era. With flawless paint depth and a showroom-quality interior, this is a turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Clean title. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute showroom masterpiece, meticulously preserved and presented in a condition that rivals its original delivery day. The exterior finish is flawless, having been kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and protected by a high-end ceramic coating that makes the paint look deep and glass-like. There are no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced infotainment system, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. With brand-new tires and all fluids recently serviced, it requires absolutely nothing from its next owner. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly immaculate example of this model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in concours-level condition. Maintained to the most exacting standards, the exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains entirely devoid of wear. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the absolute precision of a factory-new machine. This represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
