      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly incredible, like-new shape\u2014inside and out! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, so it drives like a dream and looks just as stunning as the day it first hit the road. If you're looking for something that feels brand new but with a much friendlier price tag, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
