    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 showcases the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag six-speed manual and a variable M Differential Lock, ensuring seamless power delivery. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with the rear subframe reinforced for enhanced torsional rigidity. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains factory-fresh compliance. With a valvetrain adjusted to exacting tolerances and a leak-free cooling system, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical excellence and performance purity.",
